(50,	1,	'2025-06-26 13:23:42',	'2025-06-26 13:23:42',	'<!-- wp:acf/faq-accordion {\n    \"id\": \"block_68628aa7b4c25\",\n    \"name\": \"acf\\/faq-accordion\",\n    \"data\": {\n        \"faq_heading\": \"FAQ\",\n        \"_faq_heading\": \"field_faq_heading\",\n        \"icon_style\": \"up_down\",\n        \"_icon_style\": \"field_faq_icon_style\",\n        \"faq_items_0_question\": \"Praesent ac dapibus erat. Ut orci elit?\",\n        \"_faq_items_0_question\": \"field_faq_question\",\n        \"faq_items_0_answer\": \"Suspendisse ut eros nec arcu aliquet dignissim. Vestibulum finibus ligula ut dolor iaculis pulvinar. Mauris auctor odio eget placerat lacinia. Mauris dapibus nisl dictum, scelerisque magna nec, tempor felis. Sed ipsum tellus, venenatis et arcu at, tempor tincidunt magna.\",\n        \"_faq_items_0_answer\": \"field_faq_answer\",\n        \"faq_items_1_question\": \"Etiam ut lacus ac justo auctor facilisis. Duis non est vitae libero auctor iaculis eget ac mi.\",\n        \"_faq_items_1_question\": \"field_faq_question\",\n        \"faq_items_1_answer\": \"Ut sit amet tellus id mi viverra dictum. Etiam ultrices tellus nisl, sed egestas dolor accumsan vel. Pellentesque id justo mi. Nam vitae bibendum sem. Quisque vitae euismod est, non lacinia nisl. Cras efficitur magna erat, ac iaculis risus aliquet et. Sed id venenatis metus.\",\n        \"_faq_items_1_answer\": \"field_faq_answer\",\n        \"faq_items_2_question\": \"Pellentesque ut vehicula nunc. Sed interdum malesuada diam, vitae tempor est feugiat ut?\",\n        \"_faq_items_2_question\": \"field_faq_question\",\n        \"faq_items_2_answer\": \"Nam gravida fringilla pellentesque. Donec sagittis in est vestibulum ultrices. In a elit posuere, semper erat quis, lacinia tortor. Donec non lacus pellentesque, ultricies mi ac, dictum ex. Sed condimentum purus vitae iaculis porta. Suspendisse placerat neque non blandit fermentum. Curabitur sollicitudin tincidunt vehicula. Phasellus volutpat metus nec arcu pretium egestas.\",\n        \"_faq_items_2_answer\": \"field_faq_answer\",\n        \"faq_items\": 3,\n        \"_faq_items\": \"field_faq_items\"\n    },\n    \"align\": \"\",\n    \"mode\": \"edit\"\n} /-->',	'40',	'Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet, consectetur adipiscing elit. Fusce nec enim eu nulla suscipit bibendum. Proin consectetur dolor sed metus ultrices semper.',	'publish',	'closed',	'closed',	'',	'40',	'',	'',	'2025-06-30 18:37:48',	'2025-06-30 18:37:48',	'',	0,	'http://fooz.local/?post_type=books&#038;p=50',	0,	'books',	'',	0),
(51,	1,	'2025-06-30 12:43:33',	'2025-06-30 12:43:33',	'<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>This is an example page. It\'s different from a blog post because it will stay in one place and will show up in your site navigation (in most themes). Most people start with an About page that introduces them to potential site visitors. It might say something like this:</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:quote -->\n<blockquote class=\"wp-block-quote\"><!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Hi there! I\'m a bike messenger by day, aspiring actor by night, and this is my website. I live in Los Angeles, have a great dog named Jack, and I like piña coladas. (And gettin\' caught in the rain.)</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph --></blockquote>\n<!-- /wp:quote -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>...or something like this:</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:quote -->\n<blockquote class=\"wp-block-quote\"><!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>The XYZ Doohickey Company was founded in 1971, and has been providing quality doohickeys to the public ever since. Located in Gotham City, XYZ employs over 2,000 people and does all kinds of awesome things for the Gotham community.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph --></blockquote>\n<!-- /wp:quote -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>As a new WordPress user, you should go to <a href=\"http://fooz.local/wp-admin/\">your dashboard</a> to delete this page and create new pages for your content. Have fun!</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->',	'Sample Page',	'',	'inherit',	'closed',	'closed',	'',	'2-autosave-v1',	'',	'',	'2025-06-30 12:43:33',	'2025-06-30 12:43:33',	'',	2,	'http://fooz.local/?p=51',	0,	'revision',	'',	0);
